Here is a clean, production-ready implementation of **SOLID Single Responsibility Principle (SRP) (variant 14)** in Software_engineering.

### Explanation
Refactors a bloated User class into discrete UserManager and UserNotification classes. Specifically, this handles variant case 14.

### Implementation
```python
